<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,follow" />
    <title>API REST | StelleVere</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f7efe3;
        --surface: #fffaf4;
        --line: #e7d8c8;
        --ink: #241d18;
        --muted: #6e6258;
        --accent: #bc5d08;
        --ok: #157347;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fcf7f1 0%, #efe2d1 100%);
        color: var(--ink);
      }
      main {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 24px 16px 56px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
      }
      .panel {
        background: rgba(255, 250, 244, 0.95);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 22px;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        font-size: 11px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: .12em;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      h1, h2, h3, p, pre { margin: 0; }
      .muted { color: var(--muted); }
      .row, .status-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
      .pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        background: #fff;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .pill.ok { color: var(--ok); }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }
      .endpoint {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 16px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .endpoint-top {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .method {
        min-width: 58px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        background: #4b7bec;
      }
      .method.post { background: #b85b10; }
      code, pre {
        font-family: Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      pre {
        background: #211812;
        color: #f8eee2;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 14px;
        overflow: auto;
        line-height: 1.45;
      }
      a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .links {
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .copy-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .copy-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 42px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: #fff;
        color: var(--accent);
        font: inherit;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      @media (min-width: 860px) {
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">API REST V2</div>
        <h1 style="margin-top: 8px;">Documentazione API StelleVere</h1>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top: 10px;">Endpoint JSON per artigiani, lavori, recensioni e integrazioni esterne. Questa pagina serve come riferimento rapido nel browser.</p>
        <div class="status-row" style="margin-top: 14px;">
          <span class="pill">Base URL: <strong style="margin-left: 6px;"><%= baseUrl %></strong></span>
          <span class="pill <%= writeKeyConfigured ? 'ok' : '' %>">API write key: <strong style="margin-left: 6px;"><%= writeKeyConfigured ? 'configurata' : 'non configurata' %></strong></span>
          <span class="pill <%= adminKeyConfigured ? 'ok' : '' %>">API admin key: <strong style="margin-left: 6px;"><%= adminKeyConfigured ? 'configurata' : 'non configurata' %></strong></span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Endpoint</div>
        <div class="grid" style="margin-top: 12px;">
          <% endpoints.forEach(function(endpoint) { %>
            <article class="endpoint">
              <div class="endpoint-top">
                <span class="method <%= endpoint.method === 'POST' ? 'post' : '' %>"><%= endpoint.method %></span>
                <code><%= endpoint.path %></code>
              </div>
              <p class="muted"><%= endpoint.description %></p>
            </article>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Esempi Rapidi</div>
        <div class="links" style="margin-top: 12px;">
          <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/api/artigiani" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apri lista artigiani JSON</a>
          <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/api/artigiani/idratest" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apri dettaglio artigiano JSON</a>
          <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/api/lavori?categoria=idraulica&citta=roma" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apri lista lavori JSON</a>
          <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/api/recensioni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apri lista recensioni JSON</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Autenticazione</div>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top: 8px;">Gli endpoint di lettura sono pubblici. Gli endpoint di scrittura accettano la chiave via header <code>x-api-key</code> oppure come parametro <code>api_key</code>.</p>
        <pre id="curl-create-job" style="margin-top: 12px;">curl -X POST "<%= baseUrl %>/api/lavori" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "x-api-key: YOUR_WRITE_KEY" \
  -d '{
    "artigiano_slug": "idratest",
    "categoria_slug": "idraulica",
    "titolo": "Sostituzione rubinetto cucina",
    "descrizione": "Sostituzione miscelatore cucina e verifica finale della tenuta.",
    "citta": "Roma",
    "quartiere": "Salario",
    "lat": 41.9326,
    "lng": 12.4994,
    "immagini": [{ "src": "data:image/jpeg;base64,...", "name": "rubinetto-1.jpg" }]
  }'</pre>
        <div class="copy-row">
          <button class="copy-btn" type="button" data-copy-target="curl-create-job">Copia curl creazione lavoro</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Esempio Recensione</div>
        <pre id="curl-create-review" style="margin-top: 12px;">curl -X POST "<%= baseUrl %>/api/recensioni" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "x-api-key: YOUR_WRITE_KEY" \
  -d '{
    "artigiano_slug": "idratest",
    "lavoro_slug": "sostituzione-caldaia-a-condensazione-roma-1774339190198",
    "cliente_nome": "Mario Rossi",
    "voto": 5,
    "testo": "Lavoro preciso, puntuale e pulito."
  }'</pre>
        <div class="copy-row">
          <button class="copy-btn" type="button" data-copy-target="curl-create-review">Copia curl recensione</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">Documentazione File</div>
        <div class="links" style="margin-top: 12px;">
          <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/health" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Health check</a>
          <span class="muted">File locale docs: <code>docs/api-rest.md</code></span>
          <span class="muted">File locale esempi curl: <code>docs/curl-examples.md</code></span>
          <span class="muted">File locale Postman: <code>docs/postman-stellevere-v2.collection.json</code></span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <script>
      document.querySelectorAll('[data-copy-target]').forEach(function (button) {
        button.addEventListener('click', async function () {
          var target = document.getElementById(button.getAttribute('data-copy-target'));
          if (!target) return;
          try {
            await navigator.clipboard.writeText(target.textContent);
            var original = button.textContent;
            button.textContent = 'Copiato';
            setTimeout(function () {
              button.textContent = original;
            }, 1800);
          } catch (_) {
            var range = document.createRange();
            range.selectNodeContents(target);
            var selection = window.getSelection();
            selection.removeAllRanges();
            selection.addRange(range);
          }
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
